auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c7a4dafc5134a5bf5e92c55df47fa22204c13f7","tid":1470851,"uid":226304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:02:14.000Z","msg":"&quot;HONG KONG&quot; - BDTC"},{"pid":"4970e251a5625760b23d4542d5a93c4d5c7e0a41","tid":1470851,"uid":179293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:47:38.000Z","msg":"🇬🇧❤ Support BNO Hong Konger 🙏🏻非常緊急呼籲：英屬香港人簽署！（廣傳）<br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852 / 000000<br />\n<br />\n#簽署 Sign tick ✅ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=a8d0ccd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"8fde2fdbec2dd4d4291ccef335652b780f829df0","tid":1470851,"uid":242259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T22:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brfmu41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbrfmu41.jpg&h=9450a8a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n的確係有藍色BNO......"},{"pid":"ca7628b50688dab301935d77e0042bc42058ade8","tid":1470851,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:41:33.000Z","msg":"1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPostal code 就打000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=a8d0ccd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"150906ca03bd6e10604ba2f41863886e55508be7","tid":1470851,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"求求00後都幫手簽, 對你地都有好處<br />\n<br />\n英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解要支持?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.成功爭取父母啲BNO變BC後, 因關係可以用家庭團聚形式入籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.增加香港有外國國籍啲人數, 提升外國政府啲話語權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.因中共反對, 所以我地更加要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.中共話香港人都是中國公民, 唔通你地想一世都係中國公民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPostal code 就打000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=a8d0ccd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"9d0af007a6271322575edca0524afaf87b97ef48","tid":1470851,"uid":289094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11fecf2eb6e060461fd0312c8cd4c420395473ae","tid":1470851,"uid":17392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"岩岩問老豆有無BNO  佢話有<br />\n點知個本野同網上個D 完全唔同<br />\n子女個欄我個陣未出世無名<br />\n係咪唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\